[4:05 PM] anybody know how i can bring some blogs but i need the date without the hour, just the day and year...
[4:05 PM] &lt;div class="flex flex-row flex-wrap gap-8 m-auto justify-center xl:justify-start"&gt;
    {% set rec_posts = blog_recent_posts(92930847857) %} {% for rec_post in
    rec_posts %}
    &lt;a class="max-w-[405px] block" href="{{ rec_post.absolute_url }}"&gt;
      &lt;img
        class="object-cover h-[256px]"
        src="{{rec_post.featured_image}}"
        alt="image 1"
      /&gt;
      &lt;div class="max-w-[405px] p-9 flex flex-col gap-2 md:px-0"&gt;
        &lt;p class="font-medium text-sm leading-6 text-purple"&gt;
          {{ rec_post.publish_date }}
        &lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;p class="text-2xl font-bold leading-7 text-black"&gt;
          {{ rec_post.name }}
        &lt;/p&gt;
        &lt;p class="font-bold text-sm leading-6 text-purple underline"&gt;
          View more
        &lt;/p&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;/a&gt;
    {% endfor %}
  &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
[4:06 PM] That point here brings the date {{ rec_post.publish_date }}, but everything with time too and i only want day and year
